OL,6,FThe fire at the iconic and beloved
OL,7,Festablishment caught the attention of
OL,8,Fthe nation.
OL,10,FThe blaze struck just days after the
OL,11,Fpub had changed hands, leaving the
OL,12,Fcommunity in shock.
OL,14,FOne campaigner who spent a lot of his
OL,15,Fchildhood at the Crooked House and
OL,16,Fsays that six months on, the pub is
OL,17,Fnow a 'dumping ground'.
OL,19,FWhat happened?
