OL,6,FThe fire broke out at around 10pm on
OL,7,FSaturday 5 August, under mysterious
OL,8,Fcircumstances, leading to a swift
OL,9,Fresponse from local fire services.
OL,11,Fsaid six crews from both Staffordshire
OL,12,Fand West Midlands Fire Service tackled
OL,13,Fthe blaze throughout the night.
OL,15,FDespite their efforts, the pub, known
OL,16,Ffor its unique, wonky architecture,
OL,17,Fwas left in ruins.
OL,19,FDrone shots reveal the damage in the
OL,20,Faftermath of the fire
