OL,6,FCalls for pub to be rebuilt "brick by
OL,7,Fbrick"
OL,9,FThe mayor of the West Midlands, Andy
OL,10,FStreet, called for the Crooked House
OL,11,Fpub to be "rebuilt brick by brick"
OL,13,FHe said any attempt to change its use
OL,14,Fin the future should be blocked,
OL,15,Finsisting he would not let the iconic
OL,16,Fpub "be consigned to history".
