OL,6,FMr Street said: "It was no secret that
OL,7,Fthe site was on the open market for
OL,8,Fsome time and that Marston's were
OL,9,Fstruggling to make the site viable as
OL,10,Fa pub, however given the outpouring of
OL,11,Fsupport following this weekend's fire,
OL,12,Fwe are convinced that there could well
OL,13,Fbe a future for the pub."
OL,15,FIn the weeks following the fire, a
OL,16,Fcampaign rapidly gained momentum, with
OL,17,Fadvocates calling for the pub to be
OL,18,Frebuilt "brick by brick".
