OL,6,FWhat did police say?
OL,8,FThere have been regular protests at
OL,9,Fthe site, from local people who never
OL,10,Fwanted the pub to be sold in the first
OL,11,Fplace.
OL,13,FThe arson investigation into the cause
OL,14,Fof the fire has been ongoing.
OL,16,FTo date, six individuals have been
OL,17,Farrested in connection with the fire.
OL,19,FStaffordshire Police says the suspects
OL,20,Fcurrently remain on conditional police
OL,21,Fbail as the investigation continues.
