OL,6,FCampaign to stop Grade II listed
OL,7,Fbuildings being lost for good
OL,9,FAn initiative was launched following
OL,10,Fthe destruction of the iconic Crooked
OL,11,FHouse to help protect historic and
OL,12,Fcherished pubs in the area.
OL,14,FWest Midlands Combined Authority
OL,15,F(WMCA) submitted five local pubs for
OL,16,FGrade II listed status.
