OL,6,FThe Mitre, The Duke William, The
OL,7,FQueens Head, all in Stourbridge,
OL,8,FPretty Bricks, in Walsall, and Ye Old
OL,9,FLeathern Bottel, in Wednesbury, were
OL,10,Fnominated by the public as part of the
OL,11,FList Your Local initiative which was
OL,12,Flaunched last September by the WMCA in
OL,13,Fpartnership with the Campaign for Real
OL,14,FAle (CAMRA).
OL,16,F'This cannot happen anywhere else,'
OL,17,Fsays Andy Street
OL,19,FThe initiative encourages residents to
OL,20,Fsubmit the pubs they believe are of
OL,21,Fhistorical significance to the region.
