OL,6,FThe WMCA has sent a list of pubs to
OL,7,FHistoric England for recommendations
OL,8,Fto be listed. If agreed, Historic
OL,9,FEngland will then ask the secretary of
OL,10,Fstate for culture, media, and sport,
OL,11,Ffor approval.
OL,13,FBy taking the first steps into listing
OL,14,Flocal pubs, the WMCA hopes the
OL,15,Finitiative will spearhead efforts to
OL,16,Fstop historical pubs being lost for
OL,17,Fgood.
OL,19,FMore pubs are due to be submitted for
OL,20,Flisted status in the next few weeks.
